Package com.st.st25sdk.type5.st25dv

Provide API related to ST25DV Family Tags and Dynamic Tags including following main features according to product: Password management Area configuration Configurations with access to Static/Dynamic registers Fast Transfer Mode Extended commands

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ST25DVDynRegisterEh
    Energy Harvesting Dynamic Register with following controls Enable/Disable EH feature EH feature is enabled/disabled RF field is not detected or present Supply detected on VCC or not
    ST25DVDynRegisterGpo
    GPO Dyn register Fields managed "GPO_VAL bit0", "GPO_IT bit7",
    ST25DVDynRegisterMb
    Defines methods to manage the MailBox Dynamic Register MB Control Dyn Fast Transfer Mode control and status
    ST25DVRegisterEh
    EH static register Fields managed "EH_MODE bit0", "RFU bit7:1",
    ST25DVRegisterEndAi
    ST25DVRegisterEndAi represents a class that aims to manage the EndAi of DV registers Default setting: End 1 = FFh; End2 = FFh; End3 = FFh End 1 = Max Endi = FFh, only one area available Area 1: 0000 h to [( End1+1)*32 -1] in byte (0 to 8191) bytes
    ST25DVRegisterGpo
    GPO register Fields managed "RF_USER_EN" "RF_BUSY_EN", "RF_INTERUPT_EN", "FIELD_CHANGE_EN", "RF_PUTMSG_EN", "RF_GETMSG_EN", "RF_WRITE_EN", "GPO_EN",
    ST25DVRegisterITTime
    ITime register Manage Interruption pulse duration
    ST25DVRegisterLockCfg
    LOCK_CFG static register Fields managed "LCK_CFG bit0", "RFU bit7:1",
    ST25DVRegisterMailboxWatchdog
    MB_WD static register Fields managed "MB_WDG bit0:2", "RFU bit7:3",
    ST25DVRegisterMbMode
    Mail box static register Enable/Disable Mail Box mode
    ST25DVRegisterRfAiSS
    ST25DVRegisterRfAiSS represents a class that aims to manage the Password and protection of DV Areai
    ST25DVRegisterRfMgt
    RF_MNGT static register Fields managed "RF_DISABLE bit0", "RF_SLEEP bit1", "RFU bit7:2",
    ST25DVTag
    Provide implementation of ST25DV Dynamic tags with access to main features as Password management, Area configuration, Fast Transfer Mode with Read/Write/Configuration functions, NDEF functions related, Tag informations, Type5Tag commands and custom commands, CC file, System file.
    ST25TV64KTag
    Provide implementation of ST25TV64KTag tags with access to main features as Password management, Areas configuration, NDEF related functions, Tag informations, Type5Tag commands and ST custom commands, CC file, System file.
